                             'GoFigure' 1.2

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'GoFigure' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} played on a 11 by 11 tile board. The
goal is to create closed figures using the tiles that are available on
the board.

  Try to create the biggest figures you can, the bigger they are, the
more points you get (for example, a figure made with 4 tiles would give
you 1 point but a figure made with 40 tiles would give 1296 points).

  Have fun!

